        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " erroneous, although, if we follow Matthew 23, we must conclude that this connection was first made at a later date. Apart from this, however, the connection is quite capable of being explained, not, perhaps, from the mention of cups and platters, but ",
        "children": []
